### Create a new staff member
POST http://localhost:5000/staff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Michael Scott",
  "position": "Regional Manager",
  "department": "Sales",
  "email": "michael.scott@bestbuy.com",
  "phone": "555-555-5555"
}

### Read all staff members
GET http://localhost:5000/staff

### Read a specific staff member by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/staff/1

### Update an existing staff member
PUT http://localhost:5000/staff/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "2",
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "position": "Customer Service Lead",
  "department": "Support",
  "email": "jane.smith@bestbuy.com",
  "phone": "987-654-3210"
}

### Delete a staff member
DELETE http://localhost:5000/staff/3
